    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age and mileage. The exterior has several noticeable door dings and some fading on the clear coat on the roof, while the interior upholstery has some staining and a small tear in the driver's seat. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, but the brakes will likely need replacement within the next few months, and there is a slow oil leak that requires monitoring. It\u2019s a solid option for someone looking for a budget-friendly vehicle who doesn't mind putting in a little work to bring it back to its best.",
