    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty car, and it\u2019s looking for a brand-new home! It\u2019s been super well-maintained and is in really solid shape\u2014it runs like a dream and still has that great curb appeal. Whether you're commuting or heading out on a weekend road trip, this beauty is ready to roll. It\u2019s been a joy to drive, and I\u2019m sure you\u2019ll love it too. Come check it out and see for yourself!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
