    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a standout example of pride in ownership, offering a seamless blend of reliability and comfort. The exterior maintains a lustrous shine, with only minor, negligible imperfections consistent with standard use. Inside, you'll find a smoke-free environment with pristine upholstery and a dashboard that remains free of cracks or fading. Every feature, including the premium sound system, cold A/C, and power-adjustable seating, operates flawlessly. Under the hood, the engine runs smooth and quiet, benefiting from a consistent service schedule and a recently completed oil change and brake inspection. The tires have ample tread remaining, and the transmission shifts with precision. This is a turn-key vehicle that delivers a composed and confident driving experience, perfect for anyone seeking a high-quality daily driver without the new-car price tag.",
